ABSTRACT

 

 

With the rapid development of electronic technology, especially with the emergence of large-scale integrated circuits, it has brought fundamental changes to human life. Now the perpetual calendar can be seen everywhere. Its carriers include almanac publications, electronic products, computer software and mobile phone applications, which are very rich and very convenient for people to query and use. The design of perpetual calendar is usually realized by independent keyboard circuit, display circuit, clock circuit, download circuit and MCU minimum system.

This design uses stc15w4k48s4 chip as the main control IC and uses nixie tube to display time. In terms of software, Keil is used to design MCU program and VB is used to design host computer program. After the design of the perpetual calendar is completed, its function is to have an intuitive digital display, which can display the year, month, day, hour, minute, second, week and lunar month and date at the same time, and synchronize the computer time or cloud server time through the host computer. In addition, it also has the advantages of low power consumption, simple circuit and low cost. It has certain reference value for studying the perpetual calendar and expanding its application.

 

KEY WORDS:perpetual calendar; singlechip; STC15W4K48S4£» Cloud timing

void SetWakeUpTime(uint SetTime)

{

SetTime = (uint)((32768UL * (ulong)SetTime) / 16000); //¼ÆËãÃ¿ºÁÃë¶ÔÓ¦µÄÊ±¼ä,ÕÛËã³öÉèÖÃÊ±¼äÓ¦¸ÃÑ­»·µÄ´ÎÊý

WKTCH = (uchar)(SetTime >> 8) | 0x80; //×Ô¶¯»½ÐÑ¶¨Ê±Æ÷µÄ¸ßÎ»Öµ

}

    for($i=0; $i<count($bitArray); $i++) $bitArray[$i] = $bitArray[$i] + 29;

    return $bitArray;

  }

  /**

  * »ñÈ¡Å©ÀúÃ¿ÄêµÄÌìÊý

  * @param year Å©ÀúÄê·Ý

  */

  function getLunarYearDays($year)

  {

    $yearData = $this->lunarInfo[$year-$this->MIN_YEAR];

    $monthArray = $this->getLunarYearMonths($year);

    $len = count($monthArray);

    return ($monthArray[$len-1]==0?$monthArray[$len-2]:$monthArray[$len-1]);

  }

  function getLunarYearMonths($year)

  {

    //debugger;

    $monthData = $this->getLunarMonths($year);

    $res=array();

    $temp=0;

    $yearData = $this->lunarInfo[$year-$this->MIN_YEAR];

    $len = ($yearData[0]==0?12:13);

    for($i=0;$i<$len;$i++)

    {

      $temp=0;

      for($j=0;$j<=$i;$j++) $temp+=$monthData[$j];

      array_push($res, $temp);

    }

    return $res;

  }

  /**

  function getLeapMonth($year)

    $yearData = $this->lunarInfo[$year-$this->MIN_YEAR];

    return $yearData[0];

  }

  /**

  function getDaysBetweenLunar($year,$month,$date)

  {

    $yearMonth = $this->getLunarMonths($year);

    $res=0;

    for($i=1;$i<$month;$i++) $res +=$yearMonth[$i-1];

    $res+=$date-1;

    return $res;

  }

  /**

  * ¼ÆËã2¸öÑôÀúÈÕÆÚÖ®¼äµÄÌìÊý

  * @param year ÑôÀúÄê

  * @param cmonth

  * @param cdate

  function getDaysBetweenSolar($year,$cmonth,$cdate,$dmonth,$ddate)

  {

    $a = mktime(0,0,0,$cmonth,$cdate,$year);

    $b = mktime(0,0,0,$dmonth,$ddate,$year);

    return ceil(($a-$b)/24/3600);

  }

  /**

  * ¸ù¾Ý¾àÀëÕýÔÂ³õÒ»µÄÌìÊý¼ÆËãÒõÀúÈÕÆÚ

  * @param year ÑôÀúÄê

  * @param between ÌìÊý

  */

  function getLunarByBetween($year,$between)

  {

    //debugger;

    $lunarArray = array();

    $yearMonth=array();

    $t=0;

    $e=0;

    $leapMonth=0;

    $m='';

    if($between==0)

    {

      array_push($lunarArray, $year,'ÕýÔÂ','³õÒ»');

      $t = 1;

      $e = 1;

    }

    else

    {

      $year = $between>0? $year : ($year-1);

      $yearMonth = $this->getLunarYearMonths($year);

      $leapMonth = $this->getLeapMonth($year);

      $between = $between>0?$between : ($this->getLunarYearDays($year)+$between);

      for($i=0;$i<13;$i++)

      {

        if($between==$yearMonth[$i])

        {

          $t=$i+2;

          $e=1;

          break;

        }else if($between<$yearMonth[$i])

        {

          $t=$i+1;

          $e=$between-(empty($yearMonth[$i-1])?0:$yearMonth[$i-1])+1;

          break;

        }

      }

      $m = ($leapMonth!=0&&$t==$leapMonth+1)?('Èò'.$this->getCapitalNum($t- 1,true)):$this->getCapitalNum(($leapMonth!=0&&$leapMonth+1<$t?($t-1):$t),true);

      array_push($lunarArray,$year,$m,$this->getCapitalNum($e,false));

    }

    array_push($lunarArray,$this->getLunarYearName($year));// Ìì¸ÉµØÖ§

    array_push($lunarArray,$t,$e);

    array_push($lunarArray,$this->getYearZodiac($year));// 12ÉúÐ¤

    array_push($lunarArray,$leapMonth);// Èò¼¸ÔÂ

    return $lunarArray;

  }

  /**

  * »ñÈ¡Êý×ÖµÄÒõÀú½Ð·¨

  * @param num Êý×Ö

  * @param isMonth ÊÇ·ñÊÇÔÂ·ÝµÄÊý×Ö

  */

  function getCapitalNum($num,$isMonth)

  {

    $isMonth = $isMonth || false;

    $dateHash=array('0'=>'','1'=>'Ò»','2'=>'¶þ','3'=>'Èý','4'=>'ËÄ','5'=>'Îå','6'=>'Áù','7'=>'Æß','8'=>'°Ë','9'=>'¾Å','10'=>'Ê® ');

    $monthHash=array('0'=>'','1'=>'ÕýÔÂ','2'=>'¶þÔÂ','3'=>'ÈýÔÂ','4'=>'ËÄÔÂ','5'=>'ÎåÔÂ','6'=>'ÁùÔÂ','7'=>'ÆßÔÂ','8'=>'°ËÔÂ','9'=>'¾ÅÔÂ','10'=>'Ê®ÔÂ','11'=>'¶¬ÔÂ','12'=>'À°ÔÂ');

    $res='';

    if($isMonth) $res = $monthHash[$num];

    else

    {

      if($num<=10) $res = '³õ'.$dateHash[$num];

      else if($num>10&&$num<20) $res = 'Ê®'.$dateHash[$num-10];

      else if($num==20) $res = "¶þÊ®";

      else if($num>20&&$num<30) $res = "Ø¥".$dateHash[$num-20];

      else if($num==30) $res = "ÈýÊ®";

    }

    return $res;

  }

//    "Ð¡º®","´óº®","Á¢´º","ÓêË®","¾ªÕÝ","´º·Ö","ÇåÃ÷","¹ÈÓê",

    if(isset($coefficient[$idx1][1])&&$coefficient[$idx1][1]==$_year) $day1 += $coefficient[$idx1][2];

    $day2 = floor($year*0.2422+$coefficient[$idx1+1][0])-$_leap_value;

    if(isset($coefficient[$idx1+1][1])&&$coefficient[$idx1+1][1]==$_year) $day1 += $coefficient[$idx1+1][2];

      $data['name2']=$term_name[$idx1-1];

  function getFestival($today, $nl_info = false,$config = 1)

  {

    if($config == 1)

    {

      $arr_lunar=array('01-01'=>'´º½Ú','01-15'=>'ÔªÏü½Ú','02-02'=>'¶þÔÂ¶þ','05-05'=>'¶ËÎç½Ú','07-07'=>'ÆßÏ¦½Ú','08-15'=>'ÖÐÇï½Ú','09-09'=>'ÖØÑô½Ú','12-08'=>'À°°Ë½Ú','12-23'=>'Ð¡Äê');

      $arr_solar=array('01-01'=>'Ôªµ©','02-14'=>'ÇéÈË½Ú','03-12'=>'Ö²Ê÷½Ú','04-01'=>'ÓÞÈË½Ú','05-01'=>'ÀÍ¶¯½Ú','06-01'=>'¶ùÍ¯½Ú','10-01'=>'¹úÇì½Ú','10-31'=>'ÍòÊ¥½Ú','12-24'=>'Æ½°²Ò¹','12-25'=>'Ê¥µ®½Ú');

    }//ÐèÒª²»Í¬½ÚÈÕµÄ£¬ÓÃ²»Í¬µÄ$config,È»ºóÅäÖÃ$arr_lunarºÍ$arr_solar

    $festivals = array();

    list($y,$m,$d) = explode('-',$today);

    if(!$nl_info) $nl_info = $this->convertSolarToLunar($y,intval($m),intval($d));

    if($nl_info[7]>0&&$nl_info[7]<$nl_info[4]) $nl_info[4]-=1;

    $md_lunar = substr('0'.$nl_info[4],-2).'-'.substr('0'.$nl_info[5],-2);

    $md_solar=substr_replace($today,'',0,5);

    isset($arr_lunar[$md_lunar])?array_push($festivals, $arr_lunar[$md_lunar]):'';

    isset($arr_solar[$md_solar])?array_push($festivals, $arr_solar[$md_solar]):'';

    $glweek = date("w",strtotime($today));  //0-6

    if($m==5&&($d>7)&&($d<15)&&($glweek==0))array_push($festivals, "Ä¸Ç×½Ú");

    if($m==6&&($d>14)&&($d<22)&&($glweek==0))array_push($festivals,"¸¸Ç×½Ú");

    $jieqi = $this->getJieQi($y,$m,$d);

    if($jieqi)array_push($festivals,$jieqi);

    return implode('/',$festivals);

  }
